  "text": "Skip to main content\n\nA cookie is a small text file that is downloaded to your computer’s hard drive or stored in your web browser’s memory when you visit our website. Cookies are used to facilitate site navigation and performance of the web recruitment system. Most browsers accept cookies automatically. If you are concerned about cookies, you can modify your web browser settings. In most cases, a visitor may refuse a cookie and still fully navigate our site. Where required by law, we will request your consent regarding the use of cookies, through our cookies consent management system. You can find more information on cookies in our Privacy Policy on our websites.\n\nRead Full Privacy Message\nDecline\nAccept Cookies\nEnglish\nSign In\nSearch for Jobs\nIntroduce Yourself\nBack to Job Posting\nData Analyst\ncurrent step 1 of 6\nCreate Account/Sign In\nstep 2 of 6\nMy Information\nstep 3 of 6\nMy Experience\nstep 4 of 6\nApplication Questions\nstep 5 of 6\nVoluntary Disclosures\nstep 6 of 6\nReview\nCreate Account\nThank you for your interest! Please note that your password must meet ALL of the below criteria or the next screen will display an error message and your account will NOT be created.\n\nPassword Requirements:\n\nA lowercase character\nA numeric character\nAn uppercase character\nA special character\nAn alphabetic character\nA minimum of 8 characters\nEmail Address*\nPassword*\nVerify New Password*\n\nBy creating this account, you agree that we may collect and use the information submitted by you at its sole discretion for the purpose of considering your interest in employment.\n\nYes, I agree.\nCreate Account\nAlready have an account?\nSign In\nForgot your password?\nEnter website. This input is for robots only, do not enter if you're human.\nFollow Us\nPrivacy Policy\n© 2026 Workday, Inc. All rights reserved.",
